Logged in or not, the client is shown our homepage (user story 1) and from the homepage when they search a destination (user story 2) 
they will be shown multiple methods of travel such as planes, trains, buses, etc. for getting to their destination! The user may select 
which methods of travel they want to see by checking some boxes, and the information is already sorted by cheapest flights for the users, 
but if the user wishes, they may sort by airline, or company they are using for travel.
